title: Stadia Changelog: Jackbox Party Pack goes free next weekend as new games hit the pipeline
content:
Google Stadia is preparing a bunch of new games to come to the service, and next weekend the platform is offering up the fun Jackbox Party Pack 7 for free.

more…

The post Stadia Changelog: Jackbox Party Pack goes free next weekend as new games hit the pipeline appeared first on 9to5Google.
description: Jackbox Party Pack 7 is going to be available for free this weekend on Google Stadia, with no limits on how much you can play in that time.
